        "content": "<p>Dijkstra calls this <a href=\"https://www.cs.utexas.edu/~EWD/transcriptions/EWD09xx/EWD980.html\">the purified pigeonhole principle (PPP)</a></p>\n<p>The Pigeonhole module is a number of generalizations of PPP, though apparently not in an obvious way. (<a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Fintype.exists_sum_fiber_le_of_sum_le_nsmul#doc\">docs#Fintype.exists_sum_fiber_le_of_sum_le_nsmul</a> is the closest match.</p>",
